---
title: Crispy Skinned Sea Bass with Salsa Verde, Green Beans and Roast Potatoes
description: This delicious Crispy Skinned Sea Bass  has been expertly designed by our chefs as a lighter option to help with a balanced lifestyle.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF221018_R28_W48_UK_R0955-22__MB_Main_low-cbe35ac5.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/crispy-skinned-sea-bass-63332b32fba4e0ef88f2d38d-1545a6c7.pdf
